snippet: Siyani Chambers scored 15 points as host Harvard reached the second-highest win total in team history, routing Cornell 72-47.
abstract: Harvard beats Cornell, 72-47, in men's college basketball, logging its 23rd regular season win, second-highest total in team history; other college basketball results noted.
